---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PricingTiers from "../components/PricingTiers.astro";
---
<Layout title="Pricing · flipagent">
	<section class="hero" style="padding:64px 0 32px;">
		<div class="cmw cmw-bordered">
			<h1>Start free. Pay when you scale.</h1>
			<p class="lead">Per-call against the unified <code>/v1/*</code> surface. Account and billing routes are free.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section" style="padding-top:24px;">
		<div class="cmw cmw-bordered">
			<PricingTiers />
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section" style="padding-top:32px; padding-bottom:96px;">
		<div class="cmw" style="max-width:760px;">
			<h2 style="font-size:28px; letter-spacing:-0.02em; font-weight:500; margin-bottom:14px;">What counts as a call</h2>
			<p style="color:var(--text-2); font-size:15.5px; line-height:1.65;">
				Any call to a marketplace or intelligence endpoint counts toward your monthly quota: <code>/v1/buy/*</code>, <code>/v1/sell/*</code>, <code>/v1/commerce/*</code>, <code>/v1/post-order/*</code>, <code>/v1/forwarder/*</code>, <code>/v1/messages</code>, <code>/v1/best-offer</code>, <code>/v1/feedback</code>, <code>/v1/match</code>, <code>/v1/evaluate</code>, <code>/v1/discover</code>, <code>/v1/research</code>, <code>/v1/draft</code>, <code>/v1/reprice</code>, <code>/v1/ship</code>. Cache hits still count, because you're paying for latency, parsers, and takedown handling, not just the upstream call.
			</p>
			<p style="color:var(--text-2); font-size:15.5px; line-height:1.65;">
				Free routes: <code>/v1/health</code>, <code>/v1/me/keys</code>, <code>/v1/takedown</code>, and the billing routes themselves.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
